@startuml

actor Administrator
actor Student
actor Instructor
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant "University Student\nInformation System" as SIS
participant "Email & Notification\nService" as Notification

' Login & Navigation Flow
Administrator -> Frontend: Log In to LMS
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Authenticate User
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Login Successful
deactivate Backend
Administrator -> Frontend: Navigate to Enrollment Management
Administrator -> Frontend: Search Student by Name or ID
Frontend -> Backend: Search Student Records
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Display Student Results
deactivate Backend
Administrator -> Frontend: Select Student & Browse Course Offerings
Frontend -> Backend: Request Course Offerings
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Display Available Courses
deactivate Backend
Administrator -> Frontend: Select Target Course
deactivate Frontend

' Prerequisite Check Flow
Frontend -> Backend: Check Student Prerequisites
activate Frontend
activate Backend
Backend -> SIS: Fetch Student Academic Record
activate SIS
SIS --> Backend: Student Academic Record
deactivate SIS
Backend --> Frontend: Display Prerequisite Check Result
deactivate Backend
Administrator -> Frontend: Confirm or Override Prerequisites
deactivate Frontend

' Seat Availability Flow
Frontend -> Backend: Check Seat Availability
activate Frontend
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Seat Availability Status
deactivate Backend
Administrator -> Frontend: Confirm Enrollment or Add to Waitlist
Frontend -> Backend: Submit Enrollment or Waitlist Request
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Enrollment or Waitlist Confirmed
deactivate Backend
deactivate Frontend

' SIS Sync Flow
Backend -> SIS: Sync Enrollment Record
activate Backend
activate SIS
SIS --> Backend: Sync Confirmed
deactivate SIS
deactivate Backend

' Notification & Audit Flow
Backend -> Notification: Send Enrollment Confirmation to Student
activate Notification
Backend -> Notification: Update Instructor Course Roster
Notification --> Student: Receive Enrollment Confirmation Email
Notification --> Instructor: View Updated Course Roster
deactivate Notification
Backend --> Frontend: Log Enrollment Action in Audit Trail
Student -> Frontend: Access Course Dashboard & Materials
activate Frontend
deactivate Frontend

@enduml
